         [02]Recipe 2 - Enables tuning recipe 2 for CR QoS knobs (recommended for other memory configuration in AD)
         [03]Recipe 3 - Enables tuning recipe 3 for CR QoS knobs (recommended for 1 DIMM per channel config)
         *[00]Disable - Disable CR QoS feature
